<h1>CAR RACES</h1>


<p>When you click 'Continue' below, the betting part of the experiment will start. You will be 
presented with the betting screen, where you will make your first decisions with regard to the first race, 
and then the first race will begin. At the end of the race, a
 summary of the race and its payout will be displayed on the screen. You'll be participating in six races, so this entire process 
 will be repeated six times.  After the races are complete, one of these six races will be randomly chosen to be paid
 out to you in cash.
</p> 
<p><b>
Since each decision from here on in 
 may impact the money you take home from this experiment, you should treat each decision as payoff-relevant.</b></p>
 
 <p> If you have any questions at this stage, please do not hesitate to ask.  When you're ready, please click 'Continue' and we'll begin.  Good luck!
</p>
